@for button
With the button module you can read the state of the EV3 buttons.

@example
#include "lib/button.whl"
#include "lib/screen.whl"

proc main()
    number b
    setTextSize(2)
    repeat
        b = button()
        drawNumber(73, 56, b)
    end
end
